The Seibec. The heart of Burlington, Vermont. In a small town almost 150 years ago one man set out on a journey to discover what would prove to be the greatest hamburger known to mankind.   Through many months of trials and tribulations he came upon what was known as "The Shopping Bag".  While the aesthetics of the store made it seem rudimentary, it was only until he ventured inside fueled by curiosity that he experienced the masterpiece. om nom nom seibec sizzler #1
